                        <interp inst="t18471213-name-285" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18471213-name-285" type="surname" value="BEASLEY"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18471213-name-285" type="given" value="CAROLINE"></interp>CAROLINE BEASLEY.</persName>
                  </hi> I live at 17, Mitchell-street, St. Luke's, by the side of Mr. Eastman's. On the evening of 27th Nov., I saw there persons pase the shop—one pulled a pair of trowsers, which they took away—I went down, and saw the prisoner taking a coat down from the door—I said, "Stop a minute," and he gave me the coat—I called Mr. Eastman—the prisoner was going across the road.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
