                        <interp inst="t18471213-name-286" type="given" value="EDWARD"></interp>EDWARD EASTMAN.</persName>
                  </hi> I heard a cry, and saw the prisoner having hold of one part of this coat and Beasley of the other, (<hi rend="italic">produced</hi>)—it is mine—the prisoner had no business with it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> It was on the ground. <hi rend="italic">Witness.</hi> No, it was not.</p>
               <p>
